tool_description: This API offer every basketball fan an easy way to stay on top of the latest data for all operations and players in the WNBA. It covers scores, stats, standings, and statistics.
title: WNBA API

api_list.name: WNBA TEAM INFO
api_list.description: This endpoint gets team information for a specific WNBA team.

api_list.name: WNBA Teams.
api_list.description: The endpoint provides you with a list of all WNBA teams.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://wnba-api.p.rapidapi.com/wnbateamlist"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "wnba-api.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

api_list.name: WNBA Standings
api_list.description: The endpoint provides you with the team standings for the WNBA

api_list.name: WNBA ScoreBoard
api_list.description: This endpoint provides you with the WNBA scoreboard data for a specified date if available.

api_list.name: WNBA Schedule
api_list.description: This endpoint provides you with the WNBA schedule data for a specified date as long as it is available.

api_list.name: WNBA Summary
api_list.description: This endpoint gets the WNBA game summary data for a specific game.

api_list.name: WNBA Box Score
api_list.description: This endpoint returns the WNBA game box score data for a specified game.
